nce\": \"Despite his legendary career and two dozen Grand Slam titles, it was a landmark moment for Djokovic.\", \"from\": 646, \"to\": 746, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 737, \"end\": 745, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\", \"score\": 0.999999999992724, \"rank\": 7.208709692606753e-12, \"text\": \"Djokovic\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Our community members are treated to special offers, promotions, and adverts from us and our partners.\", \"from\": 748, \"to\": 850, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You can check out at any time.\", \"from\": 851, \"to\": 881, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Read ourPrivacy Policy  \\\"Everything that I felt in that moment when I won really surpassed everything I thought or hoped that it would,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 882, \"to\": 1027, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I thought that carrying the flag at the opening ceremony [in London] was the best feeling ever until I experienced this.\", \"from\": 1028, \"to\": 1149, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1090, \"end\": 1096, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"score\": 0.9998205792733141, \"rank\": 0.00012797058253731375, \"text\": \"London\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"And being on that court with the Serbian flag raising, singing the Serbian anthem, with the gold around my neck, I think nothing can beat that in terms of professional sport.\", \"from\": 1151, \"to\": 1326, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1185, \"end\": 1197, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Flag_of_Serbia\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Serbian flag\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Flag_of_Serbia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Flag_of_Serbia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It definitely stands out as the biggest sporting achievement I had.\\\"\", \"from\": 1327, \"to\": 1395, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"However, former US Open champion and ex-Wimbledon finalist Roddick reckons Olympic glory does not come close to Grand Slam success, declaring: \\\"It's not even worth a conversation.\\\"\", \"from\": 1397, \"to\": 1577, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1413, \"end\": 1420, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/US_Open_(tennis)\", \"score\": 0.935861658826044, \"rank\": 0.027464247762228403, \"text\": \"US Open\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/US_Open_(tennis)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/US_Open_(tennis)\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I think it's each individual [choice],\\\" he added on hisServed YouTube show.\", \"from\": 1579, \"to\": 1655, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1642, \"end\": 1649, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/YouTube\", \"score\": 0.9999949114273797, \"rank\": 5.088598457313328e-06, \"text\": \"YouTube\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/YouTube\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/YouTube\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I think if you ask people, is this [as] important as a Slam, and I certainly felt this pressure in 2004 [when asked], do you value this?\", \"from\": 1655, \"to\": 1792, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1711, \"end\": 1715, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Grand_Slam_of_Curling\", \"score\": 0.9787513022438946, \"rank\": 0.02171000713600558, \"text\": \"Slam\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Grand_Slam_of_Curling\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Grand_Slam_of_Curling\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Years later, I am like no.\", \"from\": 1793, \"to\": 1819, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I would have definitely taken a Wimbledon title instead of that, 100%.\", \"from\": 1825, \"to\": 1896, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"No chance, like it's not even worth a conversation.\", \"from\": 1897, \"to\": 1948, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"If you put me in this seat right now and you give me, 'hey, you could have an Olympic gold medal or you could have a Wimbledon title?'\", \"from\": 1950, \"to\": 2085, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's not even up for discussion to me.\", \"from\": 2086, \"to\": 2124, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The point is it's different for everyone.\\\"\", \"from\": 2125, \"to\": 2167, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Djokovic's powers had appeared to be waning this season, with Alcaraz and fellow young gun Jannik Sinner taking charge of the men's game, but he has not ruled out playing into his 40s and having another shot at theOlympics in 2028.\", \"from\": 2169, \"to\": 2400, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2169, \"end\": 2177, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\", \"score\": 0.999999999992724, \"rank\": 7.208709692606753e-12, \"text\": \"Djokovic\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\"}, {\"begin\": 2231, \"end\": 2238, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alcaraz\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.4556652990048859e-21, \"text\": \"Alcaraz\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\", \"Q3957\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alcaraz\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alcaraz\"}, {\"begin\": 2260, \"end\": 2273, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jannik_Sinner\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Jannik Sinner\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jannik_Sinner\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jannik_Sinner\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I still want to play in Los Angeles,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 2402, \"to\": 2449, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2427